{"name":"Martial Art","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you use an opponent&rsquo;s melee attack against them , roll+DEX.</p>\n<p>On a 10+, you accurately and deftly deflect the attack. You can choose to take no damage, or to deal your damage and take their damage-1d6.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, choose one.</p>\n<p>● You dodge the attack, but l ose your position or footing.</p>\n<p>● You and your opponent each deal your damage -1d4</p>\n<p>● You take the enemy&rsquo;s attack but bring them out of position or into danger, take +1 forward against them</p>","class":"The Monk","rollType":"DEX","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"D02JENK2bbiHaAHm"}
