{"name":"Meteor Punch","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Meteor Punch</p>\n<p>When you strike with forbidden force, roll+STR. Your blow creates shockwaves, rends earth and sky, and destroys buildings. Everyone and everything i n the area takes damage as appropriate.</p>\n<p>On a 10+, your application of this dangerous technique i s flawless.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, the effect is out of control, and collateral damage i s i ntense.</p>\n<p>On a 6-, no mortal body was meant to wield such power.</p>","class":"The Monk","rollType":"STR","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"FRwXLnjLzvs4QqzP"}
{"name":"Perfect Technique","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Perfect Technique</p>\n<p>When you w ield your Martial Art and roll a 12+ you find your enemy&rsquo;s weakness and strike true.</p>\n<p>You avoid their attack and can choose to deal your damage or temporarily stun them, rendering them helpless.</p>","class":"The Monk","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"FrJzzYqn5La2lFgy"}
