{"name":"The Circle Is Complete","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>The Circle Is Complete</p>\n<p>Requires: Padawan</p>\n<p>When you have taught your student everything you know, it&rsquo;s time to retire.</p>\n<p>Go create a new school, wander the world, or simply l ive a peaceful existence. Write up a new sheet for your student.</p>\n<p>They become a character at any level less than or equal to yours, and of any class except that they have the Monastic Code move.</p>","class":"The Monk","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"Padawan","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"dAN7LFtwAqy4ZPen"}
